{"tid":1988125,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[人民弊的回力鏢味道]法媒：武漢P4實驗室初由中法共建　後被中國據為己有","createTime":"2020-04-25T03:52:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T05:04:46.000Z","uid":51271,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"eb339ff58c71788a16a68467f5430a08bf6b8535","tid":1988125,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:52:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=388866\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388866&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKqkErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=94bd881e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388866&h=5515e046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=388866</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】<strong>內地疫情爆發以來，武漢病毒研究所的國家生物安全實驗室，被指控同新型冠狀病毒的來源有關。法國有傳媒報道，這間專門研究伊波拉病毒的實驗室，起初由法國及中國合作，但結果中國據為己有。<br />\n</strong><br />\n法國前總理卡澤納夫為武漢國家生物安全實驗室剪綵，但原來近五十名法國研究人員，從來沒有進駐這間P4實驗室。<br />\n<br />\n法國廣播電台的調查報道，重組這項充滿爭議的項目當初是怎樣啟動。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>經歷過沙士衝擊，中國和法國在2004年簽署協議，合作建造中國首間P4實驗室，其中一個理由是要避免中國胡亂處理高度傳染力的病毒。</strong><br />\n<br />\n國際上將生物安全實驗室分為四個級別，P4屬於最高等級，中國宣稱在這裏研究伊波拉病毒，這裏使用的保護、室內正氣壓安排等密封規格，可以同核動力潛艇相比，全球只有法國、美國、加拿大等發達國家擁有這些研究設施。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>當時有法國細菌戰專家反對，擔心可能成為生物武器庫；另外法國在沙士後，資助中國成立的數間P3實驗室透明度很低，憂慮這個項目會有同樣下場。法國政府沒有理會反對意見，最後選址在武漢市郊興建。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">法國《費加羅報》引述一名專家透露，法國在合作中一直處弱勢，因為政府承受不起停止項目後的經濟報復，一名外交官承認天真，錯信中國會執行和遵守協議上的書面保證。<br />\n<br />\n法國製藥家梅里埃2015年辭去中法指導委員會共同主席後表示，項目已經成為中國的工具，原本同里昂建立的科研合作亦都無以為繼。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c7f172c7c9d000ea438bd9f6a39a0f61738a99f1","tid":1988125,"uid":653,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:57:05.000Z","msg":"傻閪法國佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2031090b5aa48f4a0e76e7e703542534c7b011b","tid":1988125,"uid":279606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:02:40.000Z","msg":"mon dieu!"},{"pid":"4f7bcc9833e6d51580fe781896708588845b3d1c","tid":1988125,"uid":293673,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:04:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eee8b012d212e1c9a4192cd205bdf954a1265e2e","tid":1988125,"uid":288707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"投降國最識做柒事"},{"pid":"c6af26afbc6cdfadfe95ca0665034a7f3f164e3b","tid":1988125,"uid":121885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:07:29.000Z","msg":"中華人民共和國法蘭西特別行政區(一國一制)"},{"pid":"b4ca5fa6cf278debabaf04776add3351d5f5c60b","tid":1988125,"uid":92188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:09:45.000Z","msg":"法國on9,遲早滅國"},{"pid":"cfea98448654558fc8ad0fb857e2939b59e43dfc","tid":1988125,"uid":110019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:10:22.000Z","msg":"法國有份畀錢起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea0367dab240e0678fb2f48660893a2e1af5b36","tid":1988125,"uid":250036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:11:52.000Z","msg":"天真大愛膠害死人"},{"pid":"b211120c7775153f4c38bb32f1c25ddaa7d04b8d","tid":1988125,"uid":119232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb339ff58c71788a16a68467f5430a08bf6b8535","tid":1988125,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:52:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=388866\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388866&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKqkErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=94bd881e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3F